Package org.bukkit.inventory.meta

Interface SkullMeta

All Superinterfaces:
Cloneable, ConfigurationSerializable, ItemMeta, PersistentDataHolder
public interface SkullMeta extends ItemMeta
Represents a skull that can have an owner.
